  </div>
</section>

<section class="section"><div class="container" style="max-width:900px;">

<!-- TL;DR -->
<div style="padding:24px;margin-bottom:24px;border-left:4px solid var(--primary);background:var(--white);border-radius:var(--radius);border:1px solid var(--border);">
  <p style="margin:0;font-size:15px;color:var(--text);"><strong>TL;DR:</strong> Professional drylining and plasterboard installation for walls and ceilings across Edinburgh and the Lothians. CSCS-registered operatives, free quotes, and 12-month workmanship guarantee.</p>
</div>

<!-- What We Offer -->
<h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--secondary);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">What Our Drylining Service Includes</h2>
<p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Our drylining service is tailored to domestic and commercial clients across Edinburgh and surrounding areas. We combine quality materials, skilled tradesmen, and efficient project management to deliver results that last.</p>
<ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:1.5rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;font-size:1.0625rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
  <li>Site survey and measurement</li>
  <li>Plasterboard cutting and fitting</li>
  <li>Timber and metal stud frame construction</li>
  <li>Professional taping and jointing</li>
  <li>Corner bead and trim installation</li>
  <li>Insulation-backed drylining for thermal upgrades</li>
  <li>Soundproofing solutions for noise reduction</li>
  <li>Fire-rated plasterboard for safety compliance</li>
  <li>Full cleanup and waste removal</li>
</ul>

<!-- Why Choose Us -->
<h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--secondary);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">Why Choose Our Drylining Contractors?</h2>
<ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:1.5rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;font-size:1.0625rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
  <li><strong>CSCS-registered team:</strong> All our drylining operatives hold valid CSCS cards and are fully insured for domestic and commercial work.</li>
  <li><strong>15+ years experience:</strong> We have completed drylining projects ranging from single rooms to multi-floor commercial fit-outs.</li>
  <li><strong>Free, detailed quotes:</strong> No obligation site visits with clear breakdowns of labour, materials, and timeline.</li>
  <li><strong>Building regulation compliance:</strong> We ensure all work meets Part L thermal efficiency and Part B fire safety standards.</li>
  <li><strong>Fast turnaround:</strong> Drylining is significantly faster than wet plastering, reducing project downtime.</li>
</ul>

<!-- Materials -->
<h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--secondary);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">Materials & Specifications</h2>
<p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">We use industry-leading products from trusted manufacturers to ensure durability, compliance, and a premium finish.</p>
<ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:1.5rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;font-size:1.0625rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
  <li>British Gypsum Gyproc plasterboard (standard, moisture-resistant, fire-rated, soundbloc)</li>
  <li>Knauf plasterboard and jointing systems</li>
  <li>Metal C-studs and U-tracks (50mm, 70mm, 92mm profiles)</li>
  <li>Gyproc drywall adhesive for dot and dab applications</li>
  <li>Joint compound, paper tape, and scrim tape</li>
  <li>Insulation-backed plasterboard (Celotex, Kingspan, Rockwool)</li>
  <li>Fire-rated intumescent sealants and cavity barriers</li>
</ul>

<!-- Applications -->
<h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--secondary);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">Applications & Use Cases</h2>
<p style="font-size:1.0625rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Our drylining services are suitable for a wide range of building types and project sizes across Edinburgh.</p>
<ul style="list-style:disc;padding-left:1.5rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;font-size:1.0625rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
  <li>New build residential properties and housing estates</li>
  <li>Home renovations, extensions, and loft conversions</li>
  <li>Commercial office fit-outs and refurbishments</li>
  <li>Retail shop fitting and display wall construction</li>
  <li>School and education building upgrades</li>
  <li>Healthcare and care home interior works</li>
  <li>Industrial unit partitioning and warehouse linings</li>
</ul>

<!-- How It Works -->
<h2 style="font-size:1.75rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--secondary);margin:2.5rem 0 1rem;">How It Works</h2>
<ol style="list-style:decimal;padding-left:1.5rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.8;font-size:1.0625rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
  <li><strong>Free Quote:</strong> Call or fill in our form. We will assess your project and provide a detailed, no-obligation quote.</li>
  <li><strong>Detailed Plan:</strong> We confirm materials, timeline, and specifications. No hidden extras - everything is agreed upfront.</li>
  <li><strong>Professional Installation:</strong> Our CSCS-registered team works cleanly, efficiently, and to the highest standards.</li>
  <li><strong>Quality Check & Handover:</strong> We inspect every detail, ensure compliance, and leave your space ready for the next stage.</li>
</ol>

